704157f-a.title: Brooklyn: Evergreen Avenue - Woodbine Street
704157f-a.text:
Evergreen Ave., (0ld Bushwick Road), at the N.E. corner of Woodbine
Street, showing the farmhouse of one, Suydam, and said to have been originally
a Leffert's house, erected in 1711. It was probably demolished in 1900.
About 1895.
Tugene L. Armbruster Collection.
